an style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">2</span></span>=<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">3</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table>(<span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">0</span></span>+<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table>ρgl)</span>…③<br>又有<span  mathtag="math" ><span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">2</span></span>=<span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">3</span></span>+<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table>ρgl</span>…④<br>联立③④式，得<span  mathtag="math" ><span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">3</span></span>=<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">3</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table><span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">0</span></span>+<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">ρgl</td></tr><tr><td>4</td></tr></table></span>…⑤<br>故答案为（1）BC；（2）此时气缸内气体的压强<span  mathtag="math" ><span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">3</span></span>=<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">3</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table><span><span>p</span><span style="vertical-align:sub;font-size:90%">0</span></span>+<table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">ρgl</td></tr><tr><td>4</td></tr></table></span>．</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
